summary.label:
GeoLocation Pro will attempt to obtain your coordinates (latitude, longitude and altitude).  

Features include: 
- Share by saving Bookmarks;
- Share with In-App Email;
- Share with In-App SMS Texting;
- Toggle latitude/longitude between decimal & degrees;
- Map your location with Roads & Satellite Images;
- Reverse Geocode your Street Address;
- In-App Feedback button to submit improvements.
